General.Name: OUE Limited
General.Description: OUE Limited operates as a real estate development, investment, and management company in Singapore, the People's Republic of China, Japan, and Indonesia. It operates through Real Estate, Healthcare, and Consumer segments. The Real Estate segment comprise investment properties business including rental of investment of properties, and management of real estate investment trust and investment properties under development; hospitality business, such as operation of hotels and hotel management; and development properties business engages in the sale of residential properties and other properties under development. Its Healthcare segment involves in the operation of investment holding, development of medical real estate, healthcare related assets, and integrated mixed-use developments; and provision of healthcare services and management of healthcare investments trusts. Consumer segment operates food and beverage outlets and consumer-related investments. The company was formerly known as Overseas Union Enterprise Limited. OUE Limited was incorporated in 1964 and is based in Singapore. OUE Limited is a subsidiary of OUE Realty Pte. Ltd.
